                    "node": {
                        "created_at": "1768755606",
                        "id": "17848424928666517",
                        "text": "A fairy-tale cave bar near Tokyo \u2728\ud83d\udd6f\ufe0f\ud83c\udf79\n\nThis spot just turned one and came highly recommended by my local friend. The cave-like interiors, warm glow and curved walls make the whole space feel super cozy. The cocktails are beautiful and creative, with subtle colors, a little shimmer, and really balanced flavors! Met Futa, Kaede and Hirose behind the bar\u2014all super fun, nice, and easy to chat with. Such a great spot to end the night!!\n\ud83d\udccd Bar Now (Kawasaki)\n\ud83d\uddfa\ufe0f Japan, \u3012210-0005 Kanagawa, Kawasaki, Kawasaki Ward, Higashidacho, 4-3 \uff33\uff33\uff22\u5ddd\u5d0e\u30d3\u30eb 2F\n.\n#tokyo #japan #bar #cocktails #japantrip"
                    }
                }
            ]
